Title: 7Ticino BF-109 Automatic Pilot Chronograph Watch
Description: You are viewing a... Ticino BF-109 Automatic Pilot Chronograph Watch The Ticino BF-109 automatic chronograph is a very well constructed watch, featuring an all brushed solid stainless steel case with a double domed sapphire crystal. The movement is a very dependable and accurate Shanghai 3LZF2 30-jewel movement with a high beat rate of 28,800 beats per second. The case has curved lugs and a solid flat caseback which makes it very comfortable in its 44mm size. The pushers are crisp and have the same design as original B-Uhr pilot watches. The watch displays very birght lume and will stay charged for a few hours. This would make a very nice addition to your collection if you're in the market for a new pilot watch. Ticino did a good job manufacturing this watch. And, like all other Ticino watches, you can expect very high quality craftsmanship at very affordable prices. WATCH FEATURES Case: 44mm all brushed stainless steel case with solid engraved caseback Crystal: Double domed sapphire crystal (scratch-proof) Movement: 30- Jewel Shanghai. Model number: 3LZF2. High beat 28,800 bph. Automatic functioning, but can also be hand wound Water Resistance: 5atm. Washing hands and exposure to rain OK Hands: Black with white lume that glows green Dial: Matte. All black dial with white lume that glows green Strap: Thick pilot strap in black with rivets. Has signed deployment buckle Functions: Hours, minutes, seconds, stopwatch. The second hand is large to make it easier to use the stop watch. The second hand counter delivers a fly-back reset. Pusher: Provided to start and stop chronograph. Bottom Pusher: Provided to reset chronograph Comes with a Warranty Card and Presentation Box (box design may vary) WE ARE PAYPAL VERIFIED | HAPPY SHOPPING !!!
